body:
Hey guys!

So, I decided to make a new channel, for the sake of starting over fresh. This channel will be Avicus and 1v1s only. It's called RushWithJK, and the videos here will be much more professional, and better quality. If you've already subscribed to my old channel, please subscribe to my new one too.

Oh, and here's my first video on the channel. It is a trailer, to give you an idea of the type of content I will be uploading:

http://youtu.be/Fe_TJtjug6w

Enjoy! :D
